'''Laura Vernizzi''' ([[Como]], 15 September 1985) is a former [[Italians|Italian]] [[Rhythmic gymnastics|rytmic gymnast]]. 

==Biography==
She won the silver medal in the competition of rhythmic gymnastics group at [[2004 Summer Olympics|Athens Olympics]] in 2004.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ve/Laura-Vernizzi-1.html|title=Laura Vernizzi - Biography|publisher=sports-reference.com|accessdate=24 December 2012}}</ref> 

